name: Nau Organic
description:
This is a pair of women's pants made by Nau in a size 6.
 The pants are brown and feature a denim fabric, a zip-up and button front closure, and a classic 5-pocket layout. 
 These pants measure about 16 across the waist with a 29.5 inseam and a 7.75 rise when laid flat. They were made in Thailand of 100% cotton for the body and a 97/3 cotton/spandex blend for the trim. 
 The garment is in very good pre-owned condition.
